Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,---------------------------------OPCN1-----------------------------------
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,---------------------------------EDCN1-----------------------------------
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,---------------------------------PREV-----------------------------------
Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.16,0:00:01.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我回來了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.27,0:00:04.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,歡迎回來 親愛的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.78,0:00:06.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天回來得真早
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.50,0:00:10.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 積下來的工作完成得比想像中的要快
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.06,0:00:11.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.00,0:00:12.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.22,0:00:14.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,外套和包
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.32,0:00:16.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思 學姐
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.60,0:00:18.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思？學姐？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.17,0:00:22.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這怎麼行呢 橘可是家裡的主人
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.10,0:00:24.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼能說不好意思呢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.23,0:00:28.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有 你怎麼還不直接叫我的名字呢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.11,0:00:31.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個…真是…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.99,0:00:33.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.30,0:00:36.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真拿你沒辦法
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.28,0:00:38.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我們繼續吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.49,0:00:42.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,親愛的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.53,0:00:43.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.21,0:00:47.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.24,0:00:50.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我都準備好了 你要先做什麼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.98,0:00:53.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是先吃飯還是先洗澡？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.73,0:00:57.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還是…要·我·呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.48,0:01:01.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,2000)}要·我·呢？…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.53,0:01:03.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那當然是選學姐…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.19,0:01:04.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好 Cut
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.05,0:01:07.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說出來了真舒服
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.85,0:01:08.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你剛才不是說…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.18,0:01:11.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一直很想說一遍剛才的台詞
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.40,0:01:13.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 好滿足好滿足
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.44,0:01:17.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說了才知道 這真的會令人心跳加速呢
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.37,0:01:20.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是個大發現
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.64,0:01:24.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上次我們在中途就結束了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.21,0:01:29.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為了不受時間限制 我約了學姐來我家玩
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.59,0:01:32.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她這麼高興真是太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.02,0:01:34.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.64,0:01:37.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒事 今天盡情地玩吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.08,0:01:39.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Okey-dokey
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.52,0:01:41.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,做好覺悟吧 橘
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.54,0:01:55.99,SS+OPCN1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}邂逅的一瞬
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.82,0:02:02.39,SS+OPCN1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}如命中相遇
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.06,0:02:10.32,SS+OPCN1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}想要確定這份心情
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.44,0:02:14.84,SS+OPCN1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}今天依舊陪君左右
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.27,0:02:16.53,SS+OPCN1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}愛上你的一切
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.56,0:02:19.74,SS+OPCN1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}Check my soul Check my soul
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.89,0:02:23.72,SS+OPCN1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}心湖泛起陣陣漣漪
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.10,0:02:29.17,SS+OPCN1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}此刻與你一同邁步
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.21,0:02:32.19,SS+OPCN1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}Check my soul Check my soul
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.33,0:02:36.21,SS+OPCN1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}聆聽心聲
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.58,0:02:37.72,SS+OPCN1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}前行吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.19,0:02:41.80,SS+OPCN1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}去感受內心的律動
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.82,0:02:46.85,SS+OPCN1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}宛如夢幻的時間流淌著
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.87,0:02:54.95,SS+OPCN1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}渴望凝望你雙眸中的真實
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.81,0:02:58.86,SS+OPCN1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}Check my soul Check my soul
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.03,0:03:02.81,SS+OPCN1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}聆聽心聲
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.24,0:03:04.36,SS+OPCN1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}前行吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.88,0:03:10.52,SS+OPCN1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}去感受內心的律動
