Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.21,0:22:51.20,SS+OPCN1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}下定決心把它交給你
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.66,0:23:03.26,SS+OPCN1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}點綴未來的預想於我身旁
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.61,0:23:09.53,SS+OPCN1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}暗自祈禱當中有你的身影
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.08,0:23:14.46,SS+OPCN1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}於深秋落葉時深呼吸一口氣
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.57,0:23:22.15,SS+OPCN1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}嘴裡吐出的卻是絲絲的嘆息
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.25,0:23:29.52,SS+OPCN1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}現在只希望你能聽我說一句
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.71,0:23:32.61,SS+OPCN1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}我喜歡你
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.75,0:23:36.50,SS+OPCN1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}這便是我的告白
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.74,0:23:41.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下回預告
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.80,0:23:44.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家 想去紐約嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.01,0:23:46.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好！
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.83,0:23:47.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 美也
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.65,0:23:50.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,應該說 想入浴嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.11,0:23:51.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好！
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.15,0:23:53.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等一等 你說什麼莫名其妙的話啊
Dialogue: 0,0:23:53.95,0:23:56.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不就是這樣嗎 老哥你下集一點戲份都沒有
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.82,0:23:57.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不會吧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.38,0:23:59.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,男生禁止哦 女生限定哦
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.00,0:24:00.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,理所當然啊
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.99,0:24:02.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可是主角…
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.91,0:24:03.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,次回
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.50,0:24:04.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,溫泉
Dialogue: 0,0:24:04.09,0:24:07.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快快樂樂 好舒服
